column1: # Location clarification: Integer values may indicate the lower left (south and west) corner of the one degree lat/lon region that includes the requested locations
# Elevation (meters): Average for one degree lat/lon region = 171
# swv_dwn  Average Insolation Incident On A Horizontal Surface (MJ/m^2/day)
# lwv_dwn  Average Downward Longwave Radiative Flux (MJ/m^2/day)
# T2M      Average Air Temperature At 2 m Above The Surface Of The Earth (degreesC)
# T2MN     Minimum Air Temperature At 2 m Above The Surface Of The Earth (degreesC)
# T2MX     Maximum Air Temperature At 2 m Above The Surface Of The Earth (degreesC)
# DFP2M    Dew/Frost Point Temperature At 2 m (degreesC)
# WS10M    Wind Speed At 10 m Above The Surface Of The Earth (m/s)
